cat.udl.eps.ep.data

Class Money

  • java.lang.Object
    • cat.udl.eps.ep.data.Money

  • public class Money
extends java.lang.Object
    This class describes an amount of a certain Currency. This class is immutable. This class uses a rounding mode of type ROUND_UP, and a scale of 2 decimals.
    Version:
    1.0 22 Jan 2018
    Author:
    Ramon de Llano Chamorro
